quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  56,75,Yalli xiibiteh cutuuka kak korta aroocal ayrô kormak
  56,76,"Ama cutuuka kak korta aroocal abna xiiba, aaxaginnitoonuy is naba xiiba kinni kas le marah"
  56,77,"Diggah, ta Qhuraan Nabii Mucammadal 4zsafeńýķo oobisne, Qhuraanay nabay maqaane maggo kinni"
  56,78,Usuk daccarsime kitaabih addal yan Yallih garil (lowcal macfuuz kinnuk)
  56,79,"Qhuraan gabah xagtam matan Yalli satunnoyse malayka akke waytek, hinnay Yallat agleyta haanam kee janaabaa kee wadô sinnak saytunnoowe mara akke waytek"
  56,80,A Qhuraanak oobiyyi ginô Rabbi le kabuk yekke
  56,81,A korosey A Qhuraanaa isin dirabbossaanam
  56,82,Kaadu Yalli siinih yeceeh yan rizqhih (quusih) faatitiyyaa diggaluk isin dirabbossaanaah tangaddeenim
  56,83,Siinik numuk teyni rooci garoyra yaafe waqdi gacissaanam maay duddan kay xagarah
  56,84,Isin woo waqdi kay fan wagitak
  56,85,Nanu siinik kaal xayuk raqna able waytaanakkal
  56,86,Tokkel Isin abtan taamal cisab kak abe waanaah wohul galtime waa mara tekkeenik
  56,87,Isin nummat yaaba mara tekkeenik Rooci xagarah gacissaanam maay duddan (woh ma-duddan)
  56,88,A rabe num Yallal xayyoysime marih num yekkek
  56,89,"Toysa farakka le racmataay, ruffu edde iyyam kee naqiim deqsita jannat le akeeral"
  56,90,Rabe num migdi marih num yekkek
  56,91,Migdi marih num tekkeemih nagaynan lito Kaak iyyaanah
  56,92,Kaadu a-rabe num dirab leelah hoxa leelah num yekkek
  56,93,Toysa qibnaytiinoh niqna kak caddok taturte lee le
  56,94,Kaadu jaciim degqsitta girâ culim le galtoh tet digaala tammoysak
  56,95,"Diggah Nabiyow ama kol gabbaqne yab, nummay asmat le kinniih agay waaga mali"
  56,96,Toysa Nabiyow ku Rabbiy nabay dudda leh migooqaa kee weeloola saytunnos